relation: A Fobbies are Borange fanart. Reidman did the voice of the Department Store Spook, so...

I made a costume of the Department Store Spook for Halloween 09. It was also for the Funfest. It's a mask with a moving jaw, tentacle gloves, a tentacle dress with two tentacles that move with my arms, and a Mr. Saturn head candy basket. To see more pictures and how the whole process came about, check out this thread: http://forum.starmen.net/forum/Storage/Halloween09/Department-Store-Spook-costume/page/1
